{"tid":2108404,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"應該買Apple TV 4K 定換部內置Apple TV嘅電視？","createTime":"2020-07-14T13:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T06:15:44.000Z","uid":170268,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6168599b23efb2c6b53aa7f85d7f312f3f8bc5","tid":2108404,"uid":170268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:41:32.000Z","msg":"話說我上年年初去咗外國就臨急臨忙買咗部Panasonic電視，嗰陣完全唔為意而家有Airplay乜乜乜因為喺香港同屋企人一齊住，本身冇乜機會霸住部電視，以為有HDMI就得啦。<br />\n<br />\n呢一年半發現用hdmi都唔係幾方便，眼見呢度其中一個好朋友屋企部電視有得Airplay真係好開心，唔洗成個傻仔咁macbook駁HDMI落電視...仲可以一路airplay播嘢一路用macbook/iphone/ipad繼續做自己嘢。<br />\n<br />\n由於肺炎冇得番學真係每日都喺屋企對住部電視，所以前排上網平平哋買咗舊MiraScreen嚟用啦，發現lag到喊，睇d舊嘅動畫個畫面都卡卡吓咁。<br />\n<br />\n到底我應該換部有內置Apple tv同airplay嘅電視，定係買部Apple TV 4K ？個Apple TV除咗Airplay之外有咩用？我見Apple TV+暫時好似冇咩好睇咁...<br />\n<br />\n同埋順便問吓Android TV又係點？Android TV嘅選擇就多好多同埋平d。係咪其實Chromecast都可以係Macbook用chrome 就咁射個畫面上電視睇？<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思有d長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af48a572bad71001311bf913bed1352b565bed9","tid":2108404,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:55:37.000Z","msg":"Apple TV 睇 Youtube 無 4K<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/6094411?hl=zh-Hant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fyoutube%2Fanswer%2F6094411%3Fhl%3Dzh-Hant&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=5a855391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/6094411?hl=zh-Hant</a><br />\n不過下個更新可以睇到<br />\n<br />\nChromecast 每個人電話電腦都可以隨時控制 幾方便"},{"pid":"685cbf3ffccf6fb1ab065401f2fe0ea81829444f","tid":2108404,"uid":170268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6af48a572bad71001311bf913bed1352b565bed9","tid":2108404,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:55:37.000Z","msg":"Apple TV 睇 Youtube 無 4K<br />\n<a href=