56e1c3fb70b1ba7deb1020a88645a725028a7b5b","tid":2108404,"uid":24,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T01:57:54.000Z","msg":"如果部電視好地地，就冇理由專登為左個os而換電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就建議買apple tv 4k好過。<br />\n<br />\n首先，macbook用chromecast mirror mode既話，framerate真係唔多夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\napple devices多又會將電視當mon用既話，都係airplay條路會穩陣d。<br />\n<br />\n其次，apple tv 4k除左apple tv+之外，仲可以拎黎stream nas/macbook既片。<br />\n以infuse為例，4k hdr blu-ray iso都播到。但前提係你network頂得順，同埋iso既字幕/聲道選擇方面就support得麻麻地。<br />\n<br />\n而macbook上既設定一d都唔難，可以參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/guide/mac-help/mh17131/mac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fguide%2Fmac-help%2Fmh17131%2Fmac&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=641d4552\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/guide/mac-help/mh17131/mac</a>。<br />\n（如果你share係用anonymous login既話，其實仲有小小野要set)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而你要問自己，值唔值為左airplay+上面呢d你冇提既要求，使多千幾港紙。"},{"pid":"36ce9bd862f2af405a8ea285ab5a961091402761","tid":2108404,"uid":170268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56e1c3fb70b1ba7deb1020a88645a725028a7b5b","tid":2108404,"uid":24,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T01:57:54.000Z","msg":"如果部電視好地地，就冇理由專登為左個os而換電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就建議買apple tv 4k好過。<br />\n<br />\n首先，macbook用chromecast mirror mode既話，framerate真係唔多夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\napple devices多又會將電視當mon用既話，都係airplay條路會穩陣d。<br />\n<br />\n其次，apple tv 4k除左apple tv+之外，仲可以拎黎stream nas/macbook既片。<br />\n以infuse為例，4k hdr blu-ray iso都播到。但前提係你network頂得順，同埋iso既字幕/聲道選擇方面就support得麻麻地。<br />\n<br />\n而macbook上既設定一d都唔難，可以參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/guide/mac-help/mh17131/mac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport